634
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:23,841
No matter how hard it
is to restore your reputation,

635
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:27,401
I will seek justice for you.

636
00:37:29,841 --> 00:37:31,000
Luo Xue'er is already dead,

637
00:37:31,441 --> 00:37:32,480
leaving no evidence.

638
00:37:33,921 --> 00:37:35,921
There's no way
to clear Luo Ailian's name now.

639
00:37:37,361 --> 00:37:42,120
