652
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:47,600
When I thought Luo Ailian died,

653
00:38:48,600 --> 00:38:49,761
I put up a wishing plaque for her.

654
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:08,160
Wishing her
an innocent and carefree next life

655
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,000
