660
00:39:31,080 --> 00:39:32,441
In fact,
during the temple fair that day,

661
00:39:33,200 --> 00:39:34,321
I put up another wishing plaque

662
00:39:34,841 --> 00:39:35,680
and made a mark on it.

663
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:53,401
